duties_responsibilities.duty: Manage the full lifecycle of data warehousing needs using Amazon Web Services.
Contribute to the day-to-day operations of running the Data Warehouse.
Build data pipelines and ETLs for loading source system data into the data warehouse for reporting and analysis.
Assist in building scalable data models to support reporting and tracking of key business and product metrics.
Build, analyze, and manage reports and dashboards for business stakeholders.
Identify better practices, tools, and relevant trends that influence data operations across the business.
